node.title: useractionlog
node._create_table_statement: CREATE TABLE `useractionlog` ( `useractionlog_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `useraction_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `useraction_session_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `useraction_source_node_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `useraction_target_node_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `useraction_condition` varchar(50) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`useractionlog_id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
